text: Andrea Coss (born 6 November 1960) is an Australian rower. She competed in the women's single sculls event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Australian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Australia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from the National Capital District (Papua New Guinea)
